msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Any tips for this hunt?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "What kind of arcane items and artifacts do you accept?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "I got something that would interest you."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "What can I trade with these tokens?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Bye..."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"So, What do you think... are you 'in' for this quest? I do not assure your "
"life in this journey you're about to come up just to collect rare stuff for "
"me."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"I seek arcane mysteries and anomalies in this damned world as well as "
"collecting artifacts, utilizing their power for a greater use."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Who am I you asked?\n"
"I am the seeker of arcane mysteries and anomalies in this damned world as well as collecting artifacts, utilizing their power for a greater use."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"I also have grown fond to magic, so maybe we could collaborate with this."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Arcane mysteries?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "What kind of artifacts are you collecting?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Yes! I'm in!"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Wait, I need some time for this."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Well, your job looks risky..."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Indeed. Arcane, the magic behind this world. With proper knowledge, you could discover more about it, but be wary of its cost.\n"
"I will send you out of this place and look for these anomaly, just ask me if you are curious about a thing."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Artifacts are the supreme objects scattered in this world. From cursed swords to precarious weapons, they are the artifacts.\n"
"I will send you out of this place and look for these ancient objects, just ask me if you are curious about a thing."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Just stop repeating the question, will you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Okay. Sorry..."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "What will be the cost of your partnership with me?"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Exchange all your requested items with something else as rewards."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Money as payment from your life-risking quests."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"You don't need to pay me that much for this and I am glad to serve you."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"I agree, but in form of tokens. Work hard, collect more and earn our "
"exclusive items to fulfill your endeavors."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Okay. I understood."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"I agree, but you should know that our wealth isn't that high, so expect my "
"fundings to be low."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"I see you're different from the others who are desperate in this greedy "
"situations. I thank you for your kind answer. I will still give you some "
"profit as payment for your job."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Its up to you if you'd exchange everything you have in stock. Just remember:"
" they also have different applications other than selling them."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "You can't get something if you don't put an effort to it."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"If you want talk to me about something like artifacts, make sure to bring "
"them all at once to ease my time."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"I bet those odd, shimmering vapors that draws out of a dead creature worths "
"a thing for me if you collect them."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Killing any creatures might give you its arcane elements."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Those odd looking ruins from the past civilizations might have left "
"something... Strange."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Raiding a peculiar structure might be a suicidal idea if you don't prepare "
"for it."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Structures in the forest surely hides something underneath it."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Swamps are not the only place you'll ever hate the most."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Don't trust those highways. If you're looking for odd structures, you should"
" walk past through the forest."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Every monsters you fight might leave you with something upon its death."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Those anomalous creatures can provide you with something when you kill it."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"Rare monsters drop rare items. If you see one of them, slay immediately!"
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "An artifact wields a high bounty, but aren't that easy to obtain..."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Artifacts are powerful, but costs more than your life..."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "A guardian protects an artifact. Its on you if you're up for the loot."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid ""
"If you're on to fast profits, I suggest retrieving artifacts and run away "
"from any risks you encounter."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Books are common, and I've read almost everything."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Don't try to sell me with some stupid books you've collected."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "I can't accept some artifacts, because I can't."
msgstr ""

#: .\NPCs\npc.json
msgid "Okay... Thanks."
msgstr ""
